headline: Tractor Supply and 4-H Celebrate $25 Million Fundraising Milestone With Nasdaq Bell-Ringing Ceremony
summary: BRENTWOOD, Tenn., December 18, 2025--Tractor Supply Company (NASDAQ: TSCO), the largest rural lifestyle retailer in the United States, and National 4-H announced today that their 15-year partnership has raised more than $25 million, empowering youth in local communities through 4-H programs nationwide.
